Máme spoustu obav.

189
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,940
- Tak, na věrnost.
- Dobře.

190
00:10:19,640 --> 00:10:21,330
Na Mango.

191
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,070
Ano, řediteli?

192
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:42,800
